                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Find the length of the longest sequence of 1s you could create by flipping exactly one 0 bit. This maps to LCCI 5.3. Typical interview angle: Track current run of 1s and previous run separated by exactly one 0. Slide window: when a 0 is seen, previous = current and current = 0. Best answer is prev + 1 (flipped 0) + cur."
